    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I\u2019m so excited to help this awesome ride find its next home! It\u2019s been super reliable and is still looking great inside and out. It runs like a dream and is perfect for weekend road trips or just zipping around town in style. I\u2019ve taken really good care of it, and I just know you\u2019re going to love driving it as much as I have. It's ready for its next adventure\u2014come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
