      "timestep_posted": 16
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presenting a distinguished vehicle that exemplifies mechanical reliability and sophisticated design. This unit has been curated for the discerning driver, featuring a well-preserved aesthetic and a comprehensive service history that confirms its structural and operational integrity. Undergoing a rigorous professional assessment, it offers a seamless blend of performance and comfort, representing a premier acquisition for those who prioritize long-term value and engineering excellence.",
