    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and she\u2019s been such a joy to drive! It\u2019s in great shape and has clearly been well-loved over the years. Perfect for someone looking for a reliable, smooth journey without the brand-new price tag. It's clean, runs like a dream, and is totally ready for its next big adventure with you! Come take it for a spin and see for yourself! \u2728",
