    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This 987.2-generation Cayman S is a purist\u2019s specification, powered by the 3.4L MA1.21 naturally aspirated flat-six with Direct Fuel Injection (DFI), effectively eliminating IMS bearing concerns. The mid-ship layout ensures a low polar moment of inertia for exceptional rotational dynamics. The 6-speed manual transmission features precise gate engagement and optimized synchro health. It is equipped with Porsche Active Suspension Management (PASM) for variable damping and a factory-spec limited-slip differential to enhance corner-exit traction. The braking system utilizes four-piston monobloc calipers over vented, cross-drilled rotors for superior thermal management. Mechanically sorted with a documented service history focusing on fluid kinetics and suspension bushing integrity. Minor aesthetic patina is present, but the performance envelope and chassis rigidity remain fully intact.",
